Then i caught a fish =) I wasnt sure how to pull it in but i managed lol. and it was like 3 inches by the way..like a baby one.Then we hung out some more..and i didnt catch anymore.Then right before we were about to leave my dad caught a " cat daddy "..then we left.and now im home for the night.it was pretty good day id say.

Only 3 more days..thats still  a long time though.=/

Humm lets see last night after that amazing story..lol.the daddio,jenny,and i played scrabble and had some cookies and cream ice cream =) I can in second place in scrabble..always losing to the father lol.
